name: Laughter
description:
So soon someone had me replaced
Now you don't hear me out anymore
You're closing youre eyes on me
And you don't want me beside you anymore
It's obvious you do liked him
And clearly you won't come back to me
I know you've forgotten me
You know i'm still wanting you in my heart
I still remember your smile
Who's your new walking company
Suddenly i don't know what happened to me
I cannot forget you
You're having fun these days
You think he loves you more than me?
One day i was your only dream
But now i know it's better to leave
